NetCom2 1.1-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.annotations
This package contains all non-rmi annotations.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.annotations.processors  
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.annotations.rmi
This package contains all Annotations associated with the advanced RMI API from NetCom2.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.exceptions
This package contains all Exceptions that may be thrown at different times within NetCom2.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.interfaces
This package contains some interfaces, that are unique to NetCom2, but not to any sub-package So, for example, some of those interface define a bridge between 2 decoupled parts, some expanded interface of the function package, such as TriConsumer or TriPredicate, which all may be used freely outside of NetCom2.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.logging
This package contains the NetCom2 logging API, which is used in all other modules within NetCom2.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.client
This package contains all the relevant classes for the Client.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.interfaces
This package contains interfaces, that are relevant for both the server and the client package.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.server
This package contains all the relevant classes for the Server.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared  
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared.cache
This package contains multiple interfaces and Objects, regarding an low-level-cache.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared.clients
This is the core package for Communication.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared.comm
This Package is associated with the Communication between the ClientStart and the ServerStart.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared.comm.model
This package contains all Data-Objects, used within NetCom2.
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared.heartbeat  
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.synchronization  
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.pipeline  
com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.utility
